STRING 5334
// Abilities: A6CU (Stealth), Ubertip (Tooltip - Normal - Extended)
{
Conceals you in the shadows until cancelled, allowing you to stalk enemies without being seen. While stealthed, movement speed is slowed down by 70 %. Any other action than movement wil cancel the effect. The closer you are to your target, the higher the probability that you will be detected.
}

STRING 5335
