// Abilities: A61X (Normal Mode), Ubertip (Tooltip - Normal - Extended)
{
Creates a powerful lightning aura to a targeted friendly unit that increases Attack and Magic Damage by 10%. Every 2 seconds the aura heals the target and conjures two lightning bolts that rotate around the target, dealing damage and stunning for 1 seconds. The spell can handle 5 waves until it runs out. |n|c00FEBA0EHotkey: A. |nType: Instant. |nCooldown: 60 seconds. |nEffect increased by intellect and other magic bonuses of Fradz.

|c00E55BB0Might - Further increases the target's Attack Damage by 20%.
}

