// Items: I69U (Ghost Wolf), Ubertip (Tooltip - Extended)
{
Transforms the shaman into a Ghost Wolf. Removes all effects and buffs the Hero currently has. While morphed; Movement and attack speed are increased, dodge chance is increased by 5 % and have abilities Bite and Furious Howl. Base damage and armor are also increased. Cannot cast normal abilities and use items while in Ghost Wolf form.
}

